Care Connect Extended Interpretation Code

This value set defines the set of extended codes that can be used to indicate the meaning/use of a reference range.

Copyright Statement: HL7

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in https://fhir.hl7.org.uk/STU3/CodeSystem/CareConnect-ExtendedInterpretationCode-1
    CodeDisplay
    OROutside Reference Range
    PAPotentially Abnormal
